 <text>
  <front>
   <head>To a Lady at Bath.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">, since Conquest is your Aim,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">I'll point you out the Way;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And give you an unerring Scheme</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">For universal Sway.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Since Nature gave a Form so fair,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Why will you practise Art?</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Which serves too oft to shew the Snare,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And warn the heedless Heart.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Eyes could never fail to kill;</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">But lose their Force by too much Skill.</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Learn then to captivate the Age,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">From beauteous, unaffected</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
